    GuiSwingPrefsEditor
    a prefs-visitor for constructing prefs-editor GUI GuiSwingPrefsEditor.rootPane is the top component, aggregating all sub-components of visited prefs, creatd by GuiSwingPreferences.RootView.loadPreferences(GuiPreferences, GuiSwingPrefsApplyOptions) GuiSwingPrefsEditor.contentPane is the actul aggregation of sub-components, added to the root by GuiSwingPrefsEditor.createRootPane(); While visiting, GuiSwingPrefsEditor.construction flag is true.
